                  "content": "Globalization has allowed wealthy countries’ organizations to feel more secure in their positions of power."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_2",
                  "content": "Because corporations are constantly worried about being undersold by another country, organizations must stay nimble to survive."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_3",
                  "content": "Globalization has destroyed corporations’ ability to make a profit."
